#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/move.rst:4
msgid "Move the KV cache"
msgstr "移动 KV Cache"

#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/move.rst:6
msgid "The ``move`` interface is defined as the following:"
msgstr "``move`` 接口定义如下："

#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/move.rst:13
msgid ""
"The function moves the KV cache chunks identified by ``tokens`` from "
"``old_position`` to ``new_position``. Each position is a tuple of "
"``(instance_id, location)``. Setting ``copy`` to ``True`` copies the KV "
"cache instead of moving it."
msgstr "该函数将由 ``tokens`` 标识的 KV Cache 块从 ``old_position`` 移动到 ``new_position``。每个位置是一个 ``(instance_id, location)`` 的元组。将 ``copy`` 设置为 ``True`` 会复制 KV Cache，而不是移动它。"

#: ../../source/kv_cache_management/move.rst:18
msgid ""
"Note that NIXL is required to  be installed for P2P transfer. We'll "
"support other transports later such as Python socket and Mooncake."
msgstr "请注意，必须安装 NIXL 才能进行 P2P 传输。我们稍后将支持其他传输方式，例如 Python 套接字和 Mooncake。"

